    "The survey demonstrated that the most common input variables used in the studies were demographic features and student test marks, whereas other studies used cognitive features.",
    "Therefore, great accuracy has been specified by using ANNs along with the use of data mining algorithms and data analysis to predict student outcomes and performance by evaluating the effectiveness of their findings in measuring academic accomplishment.",
    "The authors indicated that the sample size, level, educational background, and study environment had no bearing on the methodology's level of accuracy.",
    "A preliminary search was performed using many databases (such as Google Scholar, Springer, Web of Science, IEEEXplore, and ACM Library) to ensure that no reviews had been conducted previously with the same details.",
    "Table 1, summarizes the findings of the reviews that are most relevant to this reviews."
